comment: Duncan (SAS) clamps the arm of Thompson (CLE) and prevents him from getting the rebound.
Green (SAS) pushes off and steps on Jones' (CLE) foot as he creates space.
Green (SAS) maintains legal guarding position. Parker (SAS) misses his steal attempt as James (CLE) lunges forward and loses his balance.
Thompson (CLE) makes contact with Leonard's (SAS) leg, causing him to trip while in transition.
Green (SAS) makes contact with Thompson's (CLE) head while contesting his shot.
Leonard (SAS) pushes Irving (CLE) in the back as he attempts the shot.
Jones (CLE) commits a take foul on Leonard (SAS).
Thompson (CLE) sets the screen on Parker (SAS) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the successful three-point shot was taken before the clock expired was upheld.
Duncan (SAS) holds Shumpert (CLE), affecting his FOM and ability to defend.
Shumpert (CLE) makes no contact as he contests Leonard's (SAS) shot.
After Shumpert (CLE) sets a legal screen, Leonard (SAS) restricts his FOM as he attempts to cut away.
James (CLE) kicked the ball.
Jones's (CLE) contact with Diaw (SAS) affects his shot.
Thompson (CLE) sets a screen on Green (SAS) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Irving (CLE) was behind the three-point line on his successful field goal was upheld.
Love (CLE) is in a legal guarding position when Duncan (SAS) initiates contact with him.
Parker (SAS) makes contact with Irving's (CLE) arm, which affects his shot.
Green (SAS) sets the screen on Love (CLE) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Green (SAS) cleanly knocks the ball away from James (CLE) on the perimeter. James regains possession.
Shumpert (CLE) makes contact with Parker's (SAS) head on his layup attempt.
LHH shows Leonard (SAS) make contact with Irving's (CLE) arm on his play to the basket.
Duncan (SAS) turns to hand the ball off and sets a screen, giving James (CLE) the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Diaw (SAS) commits a take foul on Irving (CLE).
Green (SAS) commits a take foul on James (CLE).
Smith (CLE) makes contact with Green's (SAS) wrist/arm, affecting his ability to follow-through.
